## Phase 1：更新 MapData DTO（新 JSON 格式）

#### [MODIFY] [MapData.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Models/Map/MapData.cs)

新增直接儲存導航圖的屬性，同時保留舊屬性做向後兼容：

```csharp
public class MapData
{
    // ===== 新格式 (Route B) =====
    /// <summary>導航節點列表</summary>
    public List<NavNodeData>? Nodes { get; set; }
    
    /// <summary>導航邊列表</summary>
    public List<NavEdgeData>? Edges { get; set; }

    // ===== 向後兼容（舊格式載入後自動轉換）=====
    /// <summary>[已廢棄] 舊版路徑點</summary>
    public List<float[]>? WaypointPaths { get; set; }
    
    /// <summary>[已廢棄] 舊版連接</summary>
    public List<int[]>? Connections { get; set; }

    // ===== 共用 =====
    public List<float[]> SafeZones { get; set; } = new();
    public List<float[]> Ropes { get; set; } = new();
    public List<float[]> BoundaryMarkers { get; set; } = new();
    
    /// <summary>是否為新格式</summary>
    public bool IsNewFormat => Nodes != null && Nodes.Count > 0;
}

/// <summary>節點序列化 DTO</summary>
public class NavNodeData
{
    public string Id { get; set; } = "";
    public float X { get; set; }
    public float Y { get; set; }
    public string Type { get; set; } = "Platform"; // Platform, Rope
}

/// <summary>邊序列化 DTO</summary>
public class NavEdgeData
{
    public string From { get; set; } = "";
    public string To { get; set; } = "";
    public string Action { get; set; } = "Walk"; // Walk, JumpLeft, JumpRight, ClimbUp, ClimbDown
    public float Cost { get; set; } = 1.0f;
    public List<string>? InputSequence { get; set; }
}
```

---

## Phase 2：PathPlanningTracker 載入邏輯重構

#### [MODIFY] [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs)

**新增方法：`LoadMapDirect(MapData)`**
- 如果 `mapData.IsNewFormat`，直接從 [Nodes](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/Domain/Navigation/NavigationGraph.cs#120-121)/[Edges](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#274-342) 建構 [NavigationGraph](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/Domain/Navigation/NavigationGraph.cs#13-256)
- 如果是舊格式，呼叫現有的 [BuildNavigationGraph()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#818-976) 做一次性轉換

**刪除欄位（舊系統全部）：**
- `_pathNodes` (List\<PathNode\>)
- `_currentTarget` (PathNode?)
- `_currentPathIndex`
- `_ropeNavigator` (SmartRopeNavigator)
- `_triggeredActionIndices` (HashSet)
- `_hasInitializedTarget`
- `_previousPosition`

**刪除方法：**
- [SetPlannedPath(List<SdPoint>)](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#365-384) — 純座標版
- [SetPlannedPathWithActions()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#402-452) — PathNode 建構器
- [BuildNavigationGraph()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#818-976) — PathNode → NavigationGraph 轉換
- [ActionCodeToKeys()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#553-578) — 舊 actionCode 轉換（Edge 已內建 InputSequence）
- [GetNodePriorities()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1724-1742) — 舊版熱力圖
- [FindClosestPathNodeIndex()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#2013-2038) — 舊版最近點搜尋
- [InitializePathState()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#479-522) — 重寫為接受 NavigationGraph 的版本

**修正方法：**
- [SetActiveEdge()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#774-855) — 移除 `_currentPathIndex` 和 `_pathNodes[legacyIndex]` 引用
- [UpdatePathState()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1373-1503)（無參數版）— `_currentPathIndex` → `_currentEdgeIndex`
- [ForceAdvanceTarget()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1302-1317) — 移除 `_currentTarget.MarkVisited()`
- [Dispose()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1191-1212) — 移除 `_triggeredActionIndices.Clear()`
- 建構子 — 移除 `_ropeNavigator = new SmartRopeNavigator();`

